---
// MainLayout and component
import Button from "../components/Button.astro";
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="About">
  <div>
    <h1>About Me</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="about">
    <p class="content">
      "I think the story is more strange than it is true. I don't believe any of
      these ancient stories or fairy tales. Lovers and madmen have so much going
      on in their heads, such active imaginations, that they see and hear things
      that cool, calm, rational people can't understand."
    </p>
    <p class="para">
      I think these words were written for me. Shakespeare likely had a vision
      that a girl in the far corners of the world six hundred years in the
      future would hold them to her heart and try to live her life that way. I
      am always on the lookout of documenting everything that I relate, this
      website is a time capsule for my diaries.
    </p>

    <Button text="The universe is vast..." />
  </div>
  <img class="image" src="/svg/flower2.svg" />
</MainLayout>

<style>
  * {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    position: relative;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    padding-left: 4rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 70px;
    color: rgb(65, 65, 156);
    font-family: "lapture", serif;
    transform: rotate(270deg);
    transform-origin: left top;
    position: absolute;
    left: -4.5rem;
    top: 580px;
  }

  .about {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding: 8px;
    border-left: 3px solid #ff6f61;
  }

  .button {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #ff6f61;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }

  .button:hover {
    background: #e5574f;
  }

  img {
    max-width: 100%;
    display: block;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .content {
    font-family: "Palatino Linotype";
    font-size: 20px;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .para {
    font-family: "Palatino Linotype";
    font-size: 18px;
  }
  .image {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: -60px;
    right: 0;
    width: 280px;
    height: auto;
    opacity: 0.6;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 500;
  }
</style>
